### Read the seeded active account
GET http://localhost:8081/api/accounts/1001

### Successful payment: four validations run concurrently
POST http://localhost:8081/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "payment-demo-001",
  "customerId": 501,
  "accountId": 1001,
  "amount": 250.00,
  "merchantId": "SAFE-MERCHANT"
}

### Retry the same request: saved result is returned, account is not debited again
POST http://localhost:8081/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "payment-demo-001",
  "customerId": 501,
  "accountId": 1001,
  "amount": 250.00,
  "merchantId": "SAFE-MERCHANT"
}

### Fraud rejection
POST http://localhost:8081/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "payment-demo-002",
  "customerId": 501,
  "accountId": 1001,
  "amount": 6000.00,
  "merchantId": "RISK-MERCHANT"
}

### Compliance rejection using seeded blocked account
POST http://localhost:8081/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "payment-demo-003",
  "customerId": 502,
  "accountId": 1002,
  "amount": 100.00,
  "merchantId": "SAFE-MERCHANT"
}
